ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectOrder Amending two Business Risk Management Agreements with the provinces and territories
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to amend two Business Risk Management Agreements under the next agricultural policy framework, the Canadian Agricultural Partnership which are (1) the Federal/Provincial/Territorial Agreement With Respect to AgriStability ; and (2) AgriInvest, and the Federal/Provincial AgriInsurance Agreement.
